description:
When mysterious ponies made of cloth show up and begin to infect ponies with a mysterious disease, Celestia sends Twilight Sparkle and friends on a Ponyville saving mission. Meanwhile Apple Split is working to uncover Soarin's secret, about what exactly Care Package did to him while while he was out, during Operation Lost Cause.
Coming June 18th
